      <div class="view-header">
      <p>Every Thursday, <a href="/acsblog/all/booktalk">ACS BookTalk</a> features a new post by the author of a recently published book on law or policy. Click <a href="/acsblog/all/booktalk">here</a> to catch up on the latest.</p>
